  <div class="container-fluid">
    <h1 style="text-align:center">Welcome!</h1>
    <br>
    <p>
      Today you will become a customer in the online store <a>Shop with Us</a>.
      <br>
      During the next 10 minutes, you will be asked to provide some
      information about yourself and make your <i>fictitious</i> purchase.
      You will be given a choice of four categories of goods with six products in each category.
